














7.7	Chat Server: Explain how you would design a chat server. In particular, provide details about the various backend components, classes, and methods. What would be the hardest problems to solve?

Hints: #213, #245, #271

7.7	As always, scope the problem. Are "friendships" mutual? Do status messages exist? Do you support group chat?

7.7	This is a good problem to think about the major system components or technologies that would be useful.

7.7	How will you know if a user signs offline?
